*amavisd-new-20030616_p8 (02 Jun 2004)

  02 Jun 2004; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +files/addr_extensions_in_sql.patch, +files/amavisd.rc6,
  +files/lost_connection.patch, +files/sql_timeout.patch,
